    "image_with_text_wKVLmh": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_CLbqn8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q: </strong>What are 3 words your friends/family would use to describe you?</p><p><strong>A: </strong>Responsible, principled, worker.</p><p><strong>Q:</strong> How has your experience in skateboarding shaped your business ethos?</p><p><strong>A:</strong> Skateboarding taught me to look for irregular patterns and approaches—how to revise what already exists and still make it enjoyable and understandable. It taught me to honour the past while continuing to refine what I contribute to the canon.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_CLbqn8"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/sam_james_32.jpg",
        "height": "adapt",
        "desktop_image_width": "medium",
        "layout": "text_first",
        "desktop_content_position": "middle",
        "desktop_content_alignment": "left",
        "content_layout": "no-overlap",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "mobile_content_alignment": "left",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_NjQ3EM": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_ENV8fL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q: </strong>Tell us more about your experience growing up in rural Ontario, in contrast to running a successful business in Canada’s largest city.</p><p><strong>A:</strong> I really enjoyed growing up in a modest rural community. It instilled in me a grounded approach and a reluctance to think too big. What’s great about small towns and rural life is the humility and the joy of staying small. As my business has grown, I’ve resisted the temptation to chase delusions of grandeur. I have no plans to build an empire—I’m just happy to succeed, support my family and team, and provide a great product for my customers.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_ENV8fL"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/sam_james_41.jpg",
